{
  "texts": [
    "The Reflector is designed to extract guiding principles from historical episode data.",
    "When a user ends his interaction with the model, we utilize this complete interaction episode H 1•••𝑁 𝑐 as input, and then generate reflections ℓ as follows:ℓ 𝑐 = Reflector(H 1•••𝑁 𝑐).",
    "(2)We implement the Reflector as an LLM instance.",
    "Based on the predefined instruction prompt and few-shot examples P 𝑅, the reflection ℓ generation process can be formulated as:ℓ 𝑐 = LLM(P 𝑅, H 1•••𝑁 𝑐).",
    "(3)The obtained reflections are then used to update the memory M 𝑃 in the Planner, denoted as ℓ 𝑐 → M 𝑃."
  ]
}